Optional Features
-----------------

The Wi-Fi/BT and/or 3G/4G modules are not included with the |product| by default. These modules are optional and can be chosen at the Chipsee store during the ordering process.

.. warning::   

   | Installation, repair, and maintenance tasks should be performed by trained personnel only.
   | Chipsee does not bear any responsibility for damage caused by inadequate handling of the product.